manifests.contents:
bench = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "gsdmm_server"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[[test]]
path = "tests/tests.rs"
name = "tests"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "gsdmm_server"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
actix-web = "4.0"
serde_json = "1.0"

[dependencies.gsdmm]
git = "https://github.com/rwalk/gsdmm-rust.git"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.validator]
version = "0.12"
features = ["derive"]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "gsdmm_server"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []
crate-type = ["rlib"]
